title: RGP-1: Ribbon Vaults Fee Recipient
body:
Full proposal and discussions can be seen here: **https://gov.ribbon.finance/t/rgp-1-ribbon-vaults-fee-recipient/19**

**Summary**

Proposal to Change the `feeRecipient` of the Ribbon Vaults to the vault address itself, so that people who remain in the vaults will benefit from people who withdraw from the vault.  

**Background**

Currently, the Ribbon vaults have a 0.5% exit fee. When depositors withdraw from the vault, this fee gets charged and gets sent to the vault's [`feeRecipient`](https://github.com/ribbon-finance/structured-products/blob/e66d36b8ef22bcfbc00f20bdd7031a6d418f5221/contracts/instruments/RibbonThetaVault.sol#L151-L153) address. This `feeRecipient` is a variable that can be changed to any arbitrary address, *including the vault address itself*. 

If the `feeRecipient` variable is set to the vault's own address, this exit fee will be distributed between users who remain in the vault. This incentivizes users to remain in the vault for longer periods of time. 

**Abstract**

I propose two changes:

1. Set the `feeRecipient` of Ribbon's 3 vaults ([ETH Covered Call](https://etherscan.io/address/0x0FABaF48Bbf864a3947bdd0Ba9d764791a60467A), [WBTC Covered Call](https://etherscan.io/address/0x8b5876f5B0Bf64056A89Aa7e97511644758c3E8c), [ETH Put Selling](https://etherscan.io/address/0x16772a7f4a3ca291C21B8AcE76F9332dDFfbb5Ef)) to their own respective vault addresses. 

2. Distribute the fees collected so far in the [current feeRecipient address](https://etherscan.io/address/0x6adeb4fddb63f08e03d6f5b9f653be8b65341b35) to the vaults, as a one-time reward to depositors.  

At the time of writing, the current `feeRecipient` address has collected approximately in fees:

* 23.3 WETH
* 18,900 USDC
* 0.45 WBTC

Assuming that there are no new deposits over the next few days, this one-time distribution will generate an additional yield of:

* ~0.5% to ETH Theta Vault Depositors
* ~0.18% to WBTC Theta Vault Depositors
* ~0.27% to ETH Put Selling Vault Depositors

**Specification**

To execute this proposal, the [Ribbon Manager Multisig](https://etherscan.io/address/0x77DA011d5314D80BE59e939c2f7EC2F702E1DCC4) will execute the following transactions:

Change Fee Recipient:
* Call the [`setFeeRecipient`](https://github.com/ribbon-finance/structured-products/blob/e66d36b8ef22bcfbc00f20bdd7031a6d418f5221/contracts/instruments/RibbonThetaVault.sol#L172-L175) function for the [ETH Theta Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x0FABaF48Bbf864a3947bdd0Ba9d764791a60467A) with the `newFeeRecipient` as 0x0FABaF48Bbf864a3947bdd0Ba9d764791a60467A.
* Call the [`setFeeRecipient`](https://github.com/ribbon-finance/structured-products/blob/e66d36b8ef22bcfbc00f20bdd7031a6d418f5221/contracts/instruments/RibbonThetaVault.sol#L172-L175) function for the [WBTC Theta Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x8b5876f5B0Bf64056A89Aa7e97511644758c3E8c) with the `newFeeRecipient` as 0x8b5876f5B0Bf64056A89Aa7e97511644758c3E8c.
* Call the [`setFeeRecipient`](https://github.com/ribbon-finance/structured-products/blob/e66d36b8ef22bcfbc00f20bdd7031a6d418f5221/contracts/instruments/RibbonThetaVault.sol#L172-L175) function for the [ETH Put Selling Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x16772a7f4a3ca291C21B8AcE76F9332dDFfbb5Ef) with the `newFeeRecipient` as 0x16772a7f4a3ca291C21B8AcE76F9332dDFfbb5Ef.

Distribute Fees:
* `transfer` all WETH balance from 0x6adEB4FDdB63F08E03d6f5b9f653bE8b65341B35 to [ETH Theta Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x0FABaF48Bbf864a3947bdd0Ba9d764791a60467A)
* `transfer` all WBTC balance from 0x6adEB4FDdB63F08E03d6f5b9f653bE8b65341B35 to [WBTC Theta Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x8b5876f5B0Bf64056A89Aa7e97511644758c3E8c)
* `transfer` all USDC balance from 0x6adEB4FDdB63F08E03d6f5b9f653bE8b65341B35 to [ETH Put Selling Vault](https://etherscan.io/address/0x16772a7f4a3ca291C21B8AcE76F9332dDFfbb5Ef)
